    Read Pangloss file

    rez_pangloss.Rd

    Read Pangloss file

    Usage

    rez_pangloss(url, filename)

    Arguments

    url

    A URL for the Pangloss source.

    filename

    a filename for the export.

    Value

    rezImport

    Examples

    rez_pangloss("https://cocoon.huma-num.fr/data/mazaudon/masters/crdo-TAJ_ORIGTAM.xml", "tamang1.txt")
